;   notes: Combined with cia2_timer_hi as a 16-bit count; effective player main-tick rate = (cia2_timer_lo | cia2_timer_hi<<8) × sub_frame_count cycles. Per-tune. Saved in the tune's runtime-state region (runtime_state_page-super_cmd_staged), which lives in the LOAD-decoded snapshot.
