;   Raster-syncs at line $60 then polls the keyboard. Any non-'Y' key returns the user to the disk-menu top; 'Y' ($19) keeps the banner up for another polling iteration. Lets the user dismiss the 'SAVED OK' banner while still seeing it for at least one raster transition.
